
Introduction
------------

Narradar is a tool for automatic proving: 
 - termination of logic programs,
 - termination of narrowing,
 - termination of narrowing from an initial goal,
 - relative termination of rewriting, and
 - relative termination of rewriting from an initial goal

author: Pepe Iborra
maintainer: pepeiborra@gmail.com
homepage: http://github.com/pepeiborra/narradar

